item.title: CVE-2020-5368|2024-08-04T08:30:23.402Z -- dell -- vxrail
item.description: Dell EMC VxRail versions 4.7.410 and 4.7.411 contain an improper authentication vulnerability. A remote unauthenticated attacker may exploit this vulnerability to obtain sensitive information in an encrypted form.
